":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>求巴打share setting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇架喇 都講左呢種模擬唔到100%電腦手感 <br />\nbf rainbox6內設冇得較線性<br />\n除非好似overwatch咁遊戲內建 可以較線性描準同平滑度 咁就回復到七成pc手感 但都係好難用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢位巴打正解 其實hori出過幾隻官方授權嘅k&amp;m都係垃圾黎<br />\n詳細就睇link<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bOrjZGU9sz0&amp;t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbOrjZGU9sz0%26t&d=krhCVuX83pwQhsfRk3zr5L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5ae1735c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bOrjZGU9sz0&amp;t</a><br />\n簡單黎講就係每隻game出console版就本身同pc版有分別<br />\n最常見就係上面講到嘅線性（即係你用analog推少少同推到盡個速度係有分別呢D野）<br />\n同埋盲區問題（console版廠商本身set咗你準心要推certain amount先會開始有反應 ）<br />\n其實仲有種種廠商設定係照顧真係打controller既人 但係好多都係影響到k&amp;m既手感<br />\n最後講句console k&amp;m除咗xim4全部都係唔用得"}]}